data.description: Take a look at this beautiful 4-bed, 3-bath home. This house consists of a spacious living area, luxurious bathrooms and a gourmet kitchen with modern appliances. Refrigerator, gas cooktop, microwave oven, and many more. The master suit features high ceilings with installed led lights, large windows that invite natural light in, and generous amount of space. This home also includes a sophisticated office space, providing a stylish and dedicated work environment. Enjoy nature by going outside to the beautiful and spacious backyard where you can sit and have family time. With 2035 square feet of living space, this provides enough space for family get-togethers making this "house" into a home.
